            "body": "<pre><code>box.getSelectedItem();\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>This returns an object that is selected. Here is the javadoc: <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/api/javax/swing/JComboBox.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://docs.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/api/javax/swing/JComboBox.html<\/a><\/p>\n",
